@startuml Candidate_Authentication

title Candidate - Authentication (Module A)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng Viên"

rectangle "AUTHENTICATION" {
    usecase "Register as\nCandidate" as A1
    usecase "Login" as A3
    usecase "Logout" as A4
    usecase "Refresh Token" as A5
    usecase "Forgot\nPassword" as A6
    usecase "Reset Password" as A7
    usecase "Verify Email" as A8
}

Candidate --> A1: 1. Register
Candidate --> A3: 2. Login
A3 --> A5: Keep session
Candidate --> A4: 3. Logout
Candidate --> A6: Forgot password?
A6 --> A7: 4. Reset password
Candidate --> A8: 5. Verify email

note right of A1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Implemented ✅
end note

@enduml
